WEBVTT

01:42.900 --> 01:46.070
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.080
[Episode 11]

02:24.390 --> 02:24.870
I'm sorry.

02:29.550 --> 02:29.870
Hello?

02:30.270 --> 02:30.870
Hello, Senior.

02:31.310 --> 02:32.390
Is Dr. Lu with you?

02:33.670 --> 02:34.150
What's wrong?

02:35.150 --> 02:36.630
Something happened to Dr. Lu's colleague.

02:37.510 --> 02:38.070
Who?

02:38.950 --> 02:39.790
Wang Qianqian.

02:44.710 --> 02:45.430
I'll be right there.

02:51.350 --> 02:51.910
I have to go.

03:10.230 --> 03:12.730
[Police]

03:12.380 --> 03:12.790
Madam,

03:13.350 --> 03:14.460
besides the dead,

03:14.670 --> 03:15.910
did you see

03:15.950 --> 03:17.070
anyone suspicious?

03:17.670 --> 03:18.230
No.

03:19.230 --> 03:19.950
It's dark

03:20.070 --> 03:21.150
and it's a forest.

03:21.510 --> 03:22.430
I didn't pay attention.

03:23.030 --> 03:24.350
What time did you find

03:24.590 --> 03:25.150
the body?

03:25.430 --> 03:26.270
Well,

03:26.390 --> 03:27.829
it should've been past 12.

03:29.550 --> 03:30.990
Did you see any

03:31.150 --> 03:33.590
cars coming to the artificial lake?

03:34.590 --> 03:35.350
Cars?

03:36.790 --> 03:37.710
No.

03:38.510 --> 03:39.750
This is the highway.

03:39.910 --> 03:41.310
It's noisy sometimes.

03:42.950 --> 03:43.390
Okay.

03:43.630 --> 03:44.470
Thank you for your cooperation.

03:45.870 --> 03:46.430
Did you note it down?

03:46.470 --> 03:46.910
Captain Jiang.

03:49.670 --> 03:50.230
Senior.

03:50.270 --> 03:50.990
-This way.
-Captain Jiang.

03:51.520 --> 03:52.470
Senior, here.

04:01.750 --> 04:02.390
Who called the police?

04:02.710 --> 04:03.550
A cleaner.

04:03.710 --> 04:04.820
I just asked her.

04:05.510 --> 04:06.230
She said no one

04:06.430 --> 04:07.590
manages this lake.

04:07.950 --> 04:08.230
It's abandoned.

04:08.510 --> 04:09.230
No one comes either.

04:09.670 --> 04:11.110
She works nearby.

04:11.350 --> 04:12.910
Every time she goes home, she passes by here

04:13.110 --> 04:14.390
and takes the chance to

04:14.390 --> 04:15.150
wash the tools here.

04:15.270 --> 04:16.310
She found the victim like this.

04:17.230 --> 04:18.310
What's the result of the survey?

04:18.829 --> 04:19.860
There's a lady's bag

04:19.950 --> 04:21.310
with the work ID of Wang Qianqian

04:21.430 --> 04:22.190
and some footprints.

04:22.790 --> 04:24.350
I've asked them to check it.

04:24.990 --> 04:25.740
These are the only valuable clues

04:25.830 --> 04:26.630
for now.

04:30.030 --> 04:30.750
Do you have her phone?

04:31.950 --> 04:32.710
Couldn't find it.

04:45.510 --> 04:46.020
Liu Hao.

04:46.590 --> 04:47.030
Hao!

04:48.870 --> 04:49.310
Captain Jiang.

04:50.270 --> 04:51.630
Check her call history

04:52.070 --> 04:53.230
and see who asked her here

04:53.310 --> 04:53.870
or what.

04:54.310 --> 04:55.830
Who would come here in the middle of the night?

04:56.110 --> 04:56.390
Yes.

04:57.590 --> 04:58.270
This lake

04:58.390 --> 04:59.710
called Chanson Artificial Lake.

05:00.070 --> 05:00.870
They said the developer next door

05:00.950 --> 05:01.710
created it.

05:02.430 --> 05:03.350
After the building project was abandoned,

05:03.430 --> 05:04.310
the lake was abandoned too.

05:05.310 --> 05:05.830
No one comes.

05:09.710 --> 05:10.670
Hurry and find her phone.

05:11.310 --> 05:11.990
Use location tracking if you must.

05:13.310 --> 05:14.720
This may not be the primary murder site.

05:15.190 --> 05:16.150
Contact her family

05:16.390 --> 05:17.030
and do

05:17.660 --> 05:18.350
the autopsy as soon as possible.

05:18.790 --> 05:19.070
Yes.

05:20.750 --> 05:21.910
Come on, guys.

05:21.990 --> 05:23.150
Try to find the phone.

05:24.650 --> 05:29.960
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

05:32.909 --> 05:33.990
The victim, Wang Qianqian, female,

05:34.110 --> 05:34.750
was born

05:34.830 --> 05:35.950
May 25, 1999.

05:36.430 --> 05:37.150
She was 24 years old this year,

05:36.650 --> 05:38.640
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

05:37.470 --> 05:37.990
from Leiyang.

05:38.550 --> 05:39.720
She was an anesthesiology nurse

05:39.830 --> 05:40.750
of Anshan District People's Hospital.

05:41.230 --> 05:42.670
The estimated time of death

05:42.909 --> 05:44.070
was between 10

05:44.190 --> 05:45.230
and 12 o'clock last night.

05:45.870 --> 05:47.430
The body was found in the Chanson Artificial Lake.

05:48.710 --> 05:49.630
This artificial lake

05:49.750 --> 05:51.310
has been abandoned for a long time,

05:51.430 --> 05:52.620
according to the cleaner's testimony.

05:52.790 --> 05:54.000
There are no surveillance cameras nearby.

05:54.270 --> 05:55.550
Normally,

05:55.680 --> 05:56.550
no one comes here.

05:56.750 --> 05:58.510
And the highway is next to it.

05:58.670 --> 05:59.230
It's noisy.

05:59.310 --> 06:00.350
If there's any noise,

06:00.750 --> 06:01.870
it won't be easily discovered.

06:02.310 --> 06:02.870
We checked

06:02.990 --> 06:03.830
the weather forecast yesterday.

06:04.030 --> 06:05.510
From yesterday afternoon to midnight,

06:05.750 --> 06:06.670
there was no windy weather

06:06.790 --> 06:07.710
near the Chanson Artificial Lake.

06:08.020 --> 06:10.270
So we excluded the possibility

06:10.430 --> 06:10.950
of the weather moving

06:11.070 --> 06:11.790
the body in the water.

06:11.910 --> 06:13.070
Guess where

06:13.190 --> 06:14.600
Wang Qianqian's phone signal

06:14.600 --> 06:15.190
last appeared?

06:16.390 --> 06:17.750
In the artificial lake.

06:18.510 --> 06:19.510
We've arranged someone to fish it.

06:19.630 --> 06:20.500
Once it's found,

06:20.680 --> 06:21.590
the data will be recovered immediately.

06:23.230 --> 06:23.990
What did the forensic say?

06:24.480 --> 06:25.430
The forensic said

06:25.550 --> 06:27.470
it's consistent with death from mechanical asphyxiation.

06:25.890 --> 06:27.310
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

06:27.390 --> 06:32.380
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

06:28.150 --> 06:29.430
The specific cause of death

06:29.720 --> 06:31.430
still needs relevant investigation.

06:33.590 --> 06:34.630
When will the results be out?

06:36.590 --> 06:37.670
It'll take a while.

06:40.310 --> 06:41.150
On-site investigation

06:40.390 --> 06:46.650
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

06:41.710 --> 06:43.590
didn't find any hair or fingerprints.

06:44.030 --> 06:44.750
But there's a footprint.

06:45.510 --> 06:45.909
Hao,

06:45.909 --> 06:46.710
bring up the footprint.

06:48.150 --> 06:48.909
The footprint

06:49.150 --> 06:50.310
is between

06:50.390 --> 06:51.790
size 42 to 44.

06:52.030 --> 06:53.040
Interestingly, the center of gravity

06:53.190 --> 06:53.830
is toward the back.

06:54.750 --> 06:55.360
The edges are blurry,

06:55.510 --> 06:56.470
especially with scuff marks

06:56.950 --> 06:57.710
at the front.

06:58.470 --> 07:00.350
It's typical of wearing shoes bigger than one's size.

07:01.750 --> 07:02.590
In other words,

07:03.120 --> 07:04.510
so far,

07:05.030 --> 07:06.390
we don't know

07:06.510 --> 07:07.550
the killer's body features at all?

07:08.470 --> 07:09.350
So far.

07:11.990 --> 07:13.030
I hope everyone can

07:13.590 --> 07:14.790
attach importance to this murder case's

07:15.150 --> 07:16.830
prime 72 hours.

07:17.030 --> 07:17.870
Pull yourselves together.

07:18.040 --> 07:19.350
Find as many clues as you can.

07:19.630 --> 07:19.990
Okay?

07:20.830 --> 07:22.710
You'll be in charge of the artificial lake.

07:23.060 --> 07:24.390
Get all the surveillance cameras out,

07:24.630 --> 07:25.390
including civilian cameras

07:25.510 --> 07:26.870
on the streets going towards the city.

07:27.150 --> 07:27.590
Got it.

07:28.340 --> 07:29.350
Urge the forensic doctor.

07:29.510 --> 07:30.420
I need to know

07:30.550 --> 07:32.550
the exact time of Wang Qianqian's death.

07:32.830 --> 07:33.230
Understood.

07:33.909 --> 07:34.710
Anything else?

07:35.790 --> 07:36.150
No.

07:36.870 --> 07:37.159
Go on.

07:37.270 --> 07:37.710
Get to work.

07:41.110 --> 07:41.510
Qin Yue.

07:42.790 --> 07:43.390
Follow me.

07:47.380 --> 07:50.150
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

07:50.430 --> 07:50.790
Everyone,

07:52.150 --> 07:53.560
the police will come

07:53.950 --> 07:55.190
to find out about Wang Qianqian.

07:56.510 --> 07:59.110
You have to tell the truth.

08:00.030 --> 08:00.870
Don't hold back.

08:02.350 --> 08:03.710
But in private,

08:04.510 --> 08:06.430
tell all your department

08:06.470 --> 08:07.230
subordinates

08:07.830 --> 08:08.630
to not make wild guesses

08:08.950 --> 08:09.470
or ask around.

08:11.830 --> 08:12.630
Why did this

08:12.670 --> 08:13.830
suddenly happen?

08:14.910 --> 08:15.350
Qiao,

08:15.990 --> 08:16.870
Lu Yan and Wang Qianqian

08:16.950 --> 08:17.920
were best friends.

08:18.630 --> 08:20.190
Since this happened,

08:21.590 --> 08:22.430
you must

08:23.110 --> 08:24.190
pay more attention to Lu Yan.

08:26.070 --> 08:27.070
I have an appointment with Director Sun.

08:27.310 --> 08:27.860
I’ll go to Lu Yan’s home

08:27.950 --> 08:29.070
after work.

08:39.750 --> 08:40.070
Yan.

08:40.110 --> 08:40.470
Lu.

08:42.590 --> 08:43.070
Lu.

08:44.350 --> 08:45.340
I told you to rest at home.

08:45.470 --> 08:46.230
Why are you here?

08:46.430 --> 08:47.350
I have patients.

08:51.190 --> 08:52.310
I'm going to do my rounds.

08:58.480 --> 08:58.910
Dr. Han.

08:59.550 --> 09:00.110
Should we force Lu

09:00.150 --> 09:01.350
to rest?

09:02.230 --> 09:02.750
Yeah.

09:02.820 --> 09:04.230
How can she work like this?

09:10.790 --> 09:11.230
Here.

09:11.310 --> 09:12.190
Stop her surgeries

09:12.670 --> 09:13.870
for these days.

09:14.150 --> 09:15.110
You and Huang replace her.

09:15.510 --> 09:15.950
Okay.

09:16.590 --> 09:17.430
Matron Qiao,

09:18.630 --> 09:20.030
keep an eye on her.

09:20.790 --> 09:21.710
See if she can

09:21.910 --> 09:23.030
complete her rounds

09:23.150 --> 09:24.070
and pre-surgery visits.

09:24.430 --> 09:25.470
If possible,

09:26.540 --> 09:27.630
let her work

09:28.620 --> 09:29.750
without doing surgeries.

09:31.150 --> 09:31.670
Got it.

09:32.470 --> 09:33.430
Under such circumstances,

09:33.430 --> 09:34.550
leaving her alone at home

09:35.240 --> 09:36.190
would be worrisome too.

09:40.790 --> 09:41.120
Hello.

09:42.750 --> 09:43.270
Captain Jiang.

09:45.070 --> 09:45.630
Okay.

09:46.470 --> 09:46.710
Okay.

09:46.950 --> 09:47.710
Then see you

09:48.070 --> 09:49.320
in the third-floor conference room.

09:52.910 --> 09:53.670
The police are here.

09:54.630 --> 09:55.260
Get ready.

09:55.590 --> 09:56.430
Go to the conference room.

09:57.950 --> 09:58.670
Yesterday, Qianqian

09:58.670 --> 09:59.870
got off work earlier than me,

10:00.510 --> 10:01.310
but she

10:01.590 --> 10:02.150
helped me take

10:02.150 --> 10:02.960
an emergency patient.

10:03.630 --> 10:04.910
After she left the hospital,

10:05.550 --> 10:06.960
we didn't contact each other.

10:07.740 --> 10:08.030
Yes.

10:08.270 --> 10:09.270
Wang Qianqian and Huang Wei

10:09.350 --> 10:10.430
came to the emergency room to help.

10:11.710 --> 10:12.550
It was around

10:12.590 --> 10:13.590
10 P.M.

10:13.710 --> 10:14.270
Because I sent her

10:14.320 --> 10:14.990
a WeChat message

10:14.990 --> 10:15.550
and told her

10:15.550 --> 10:16.790
the patient has been stabilized.

10:17.510 --> 10:18.430
She replied to me.

10:18.950 --> 10:19.990
Around 10 P.M.?

10:21.310 --> 10:21.910
When exactly

10:22.030 --> 10:22.900
did she leave?

10:23.950 --> 10:25.790
I think she left

10:26.190 --> 10:27.990
around 8:30 at night.

10:28.230 --> 10:28.470
Oh,

10:28.600 --> 10:29.870
she left with Qiao Rui.

10:30.390 --> 10:30.910
Yes.

10:31.870 --> 10:32.910
Wang Qianqian and I

10:33.070 --> 10:34.310
took the bus to get off work.

10:34.910 --> 10:36.140
We both took route 396.

10:36.550 --> 10:37.630
It's at the hospital entrance.

10:38.510 --> 10:39.670
But I didn't pay attention

10:40.550 --> 10:41.510
to the exact time.

10:43.270 --> 10:44.110
I only remember

10:44.830 --> 10:46.590
she always got off at Xincheng Garden.

10:47.470 --> 10:48.430
I got off at Linhe Intersection,

10:49.380 --> 10:50.270
three stops before her.

10:53.750 --> 10:54.270
I'm here.

10:54.390 --> 10:55.110
Bye. Bye.

10:55.710 --> 10:56.550
See you tomorrow.

11:00.230 --> 11:00.830
Bye.

11:04.230 --> 11:05.110
Matron Qiao,

11:05.510 --> 11:06.750
did Wang Qianqian

11:06.840 --> 11:08.430
have any emotional changes

11:09.430 --> 11:10.000
recently

11:10.430 --> 11:11.150
or

11:11.630 --> 11:12.510
did something happen?

11:13.670 --> 11:14.550
Or did she

11:14.710 --> 11:15.750
have any conflicts in the hospital?

11:17.710 --> 11:18.550
Absolutely not.

11:19.240 --> 11:20.990
Qianqian was quite cheerful.

11:22.950 --> 11:24.430
She was a bit clumsy,

11:24.510 --> 11:25.750
but everyone could tolerate her.

11:26.140 --> 11:27.590
Matron Qiao

11:28.230 --> 11:29.350
was the one who trained her,

11:29.590 --> 11:30.510
so she occasionally critiqued her,

11:30.830 --> 11:31.870
but it was for her own good.

11:32.790 --> 11:33.350
She

11:33.630 --> 11:35.310
rarely had conflicts with patients.

11:36.150 --> 11:36.830
But her boyfriend

11:36.950 --> 11:37.830
is a jerk.

11:38.270 --> 11:39.310
He's controlling.

11:40.630 --> 11:41.430
Once,

11:41.590 --> 11:42.350
I saw them

11:42.430 --> 11:43.430
arguing at the door.

11:43.990 --> 11:45.190
Lu Yan protected her.

11:45.630 --> 11:45.950
Yes.

11:47.430 --> 11:49.070
Lu Yan knows

11:49.230 --> 11:50.150
Wang Qianqian the best.

11:51.140 --> 11:52.030
We all know

11:52.310 --> 11:53.150
their relationship

11:53.590 --> 11:54.270
was very close.

11:55.110 --> 11:56.950
Lu Yan is in the hospital now.

11:57.950 --> 11:59.430
But her condition

11:59.590 --> 12:00.350
is very bad.

12:00.790 --> 12:01.430
She might not be able to

12:01.550 --> 12:02.790
answer your questions.

12:03.590 --> 12:05.030
We've stopped her surgeries,

12:05.670 --> 12:07.070
but we still let her work.

12:08.550 --> 12:10.630
We want to distract her.

12:11.310 --> 12:12.070
I'm afraid she'll take it too hard.

12:13.310 --> 12:14.190
Should I call her over?

12:16.310 --> 12:16.910
Yes.

12:19.320 --> 12:20.140
Dr. Lu, you...

12:21.070 --> 12:21.630
Are you okay?

12:24.830 --> 12:25.270
Lu Yan.

12:25.710 --> 12:26.470
Here is the thing.

12:27.150 --> 12:29.380
We want to ask you

12:29.790 --> 12:30.830
about Wang Qianqian.

12:31.830 --> 12:32.310
Is that okay?

12:34.990 --> 12:35.390
Yes.

12:41.270 --> 12:41.950
We

12:42.150 --> 12:43.990
saw Wang Qianqian's call log.

12:45.230 --> 12:46.030
The last call

12:46.190 --> 12:46.990
was to you.

12:49.150 --> 12:49.590
Right?

13:00.790 --> 13:01.550
Actually,

13:01.830 --> 13:03.150
this phone didn't connect.

13:03.950 --> 13:05.030
Why didn't you answer?

13:06.270 --> 13:07.350
My phone

13:09.390 --> 13:10.830
was on silent. I didn't hear it.

13:11.380 --> 13:12.990
[Wang Qianqian] [Answer] [Decline]

13:14.410 --> 13:16.270
[Wang Qianqian] [Answer] [Decline]

13:17.510 --> 13:18.070
When did you

13:18.070 --> 13:18.990
see the missed call?

13:21.670 --> 13:23.470
It was when you

13:23.710 --> 13:24.870
called Officer Jiang.

13:26.150 --> 13:27.670
That's when I saw Qianqian's call

13:27.750 --> 13:28.190
and...

13:30.310 --> 13:31.150
And a WeChat message.

13:34.070 --> 13:35.470
What's the content of the message?

13:37.710 --> 13:38.230
She said...

13:43.390 --> 13:44.670
"Lu Yan, help me."

13:46.720 --> 13:47.310
When was it?

13:53.630 --> 13:54.260
At

13:54.990 --> 13:56.390
23:14 P.M.

13:57.440 --> 13:58.910
Can I check your phone?

13:59.390 --> 14:00.030
Well...

14:02.270 --> 14:03.670
We understand the situation.

14:05.630 --> 14:06.510
You...

14:07.030 --> 14:08.230
It's because of me, right?

14:09.870 --> 14:10.270
What?

14:10.990 --> 14:12.030
It's because of me.

14:13.150 --> 14:14.110
It's because I didn't

14:14.240 --> 14:15.510
answer her call,

14:15.630 --> 14:16.470
so she...

14:17.150 --> 14:18.070
No, you can't think like that.

14:18.240 --> 14:19.260
It has nothing to do with you.

14:19.260 --> 14:19.670
We...

14:19.710 --> 14:20.350
Twice.

14:22.150 --> 14:23.990
She asked me for help twice,

14:26.270 --> 14:27.350
but I didn't answer.

14:35.390 --> 14:36.720
Did she

14:36.830 --> 14:37.540
come to you every time

14:37.590 --> 14:38.510
she had these problems?

14:40.350 --> 14:42.190
She'd usually

14:42.910 --> 14:44.710
come to me immediately.

14:45.430 --> 14:46.150
But this time,

14:46.310 --> 14:48.430
I didn't reply to her immediately.

14:48.550 --> 14:49.910
So it's all my fault.

14:50.230 --> 14:50.950
I'm sorry.

14:51.550 --> 14:52.310
I'm sorry.

14:55.710 --> 14:56.310
Sorry.

14:59.310 --> 15:00.790
Can you tell us more?

15:03.630 --> 15:04.110
Enough.

15:05.720 --> 15:06.270
Stop asking.

15:21.830 --> 15:22.190
Lu.

15:23.390 --> 15:24.630
Go back and rest.

15:23.510 --> 15:28.670
[Take Care of Health]

15:26.190 --> 15:26.670
I’m fine.

15:30.110 --> 15:30.590
Lu Yan.

15:43.510 --> 15:44.140
Lu Yan.

15:55.830 --> 15:56.430
Captain Jiang.

15:58.550 --> 15:59.190
I entrust this to you.

16:01.270 --> 16:01.870
Don't worry.

16:15.040 --> 16:15.660
Dr. Han,

16:17.430 --> 16:18.580
Lu Yan

16:18.910 --> 16:19.990
is emotionally unstable.

16:20.430 --> 16:21.470
Please take care of her.

16:22.070 --> 16:23.670
Let me know if you need anything.

16:24.510 --> 16:25.030
Don't worry.

16:25.710 --> 16:26.900
We'll take good care of her.

16:28.590 --> 16:29.030
Thank you.

16:30.330 --> 16:35.880
[Blood Purification Center] [Pathology Department]

16:30.910 --> 16:31.470
These are the points

16:31.550 --> 16:32.430
from today that I think are important.

16:32.510 --> 16:33.140
Take a look.

16:35.990 --> 16:44.590
[Joyfully and Healthily Reside in Ninghai]

16:38.310 --> 16:38.670
Hello.

16:42.110 --> 16:42.470
Senior.

16:42.510 --> 16:42.910
Wang Qianqian's

16:43.030 --> 16:44.070
diatom test report is out.

16:47.510 --> 16:48.540
Okay, got it. Bye.

16:49.320 --> 16:51.880
[Serve the Public as Police; Enforce the Law for the People]

17:02.390 --> 17:02.870
Captain Jiang,

17:03.430 --> 17:05.510
this is Wang Qianqian's autopsy report.

17:06.869 --> 17:08.550
According to the test report,

17:08.670 --> 17:09.950
the anesthetics in Wang Qianqian's body

17:10.069 --> 17:10.790
is called sevoflurane.

17:11.109 --> 17:12.430
It's not a regulated medicine.

17:12.550 --> 17:13.190
It's just a prescription.

17:13.349 --> 17:14.190
There are many purchasing channels.

17:14.470 --> 17:15.630
The cleaner called the police at 23:50 P.M.

17:15.670 --> 17:16.790
after finding

17:16.829 --> 17:17.240
Wang Qianqian's body.

17:17.440 --> 17:18.310
So, the time of death was

17:18.470 --> 17:18.950
between 23 o'clock

17:19.099 --> 17:20.190
and 23:50.

17:23.069 --> 17:23.990
Past 11?

17:27.750 --> 17:28.160
Anything else?

17:29.270 --> 17:30.150
We've checked.

17:30.230 --> 17:31.150
There are no surveillance cameras

17:31.190 --> 17:32.790
within two kilometers of the artificial lake.

17:32.950 --> 17:33.870
We also found

17:33.870 --> 17:35.070
the surveillance footage

17:35.190 --> 17:35.790
of Wang Qianqian's complex.

17:35.950 --> 17:36.950
According to the video,

17:37.110 --> 17:37.510
that night,

17:37.630 --> 17:38.390
she didn't enter

17:38.430 --> 17:39.190
or exit the complex.

17:39.630 --> 17:40.110
This means

17:40.110 --> 17:41.230
she was taken away

17:41.230 --> 17:41.830
on her way back.

17:42.150 --> 17:42.440
Yes.

17:42.910 --> 17:43.670
Wang Qianqian's phone

17:43.790 --> 17:44.550
has been salvaged.

17:44.710 --> 17:45.910
We're recovering the data.

17:48.910 --> 17:50.670
Find out the source of the anesthetic

17:51.270 --> 17:52.430
and find Wang Qianqian's

17:52.550 --> 17:53.270
boyfriend.

17:53.950 --> 17:54.990
See if he has any motive.

17:55.750 --> 17:56.030
Understood.

17:57.630 --> 17:58.030
Qin Yue,

17:58.460 --> 17:59.270
go check all the routes

17:59.630 --> 18:02.200
from the hospital

18:02.620 --> 18:03.390
to Wang Qianqian's home

18:03.950 --> 18:04.630
and see which section

18:04.720 --> 18:05.470
has the potential for criminal activity.

18:06.990 --> 18:07.350
Let's begin.

18:07.710 --> 18:08.030
Okay.

18:19.040 --> 18:19.950
[Ninghai City Hospital Directory]

18:20.430 --> 18:21.030
Next.

18:21.350 --> 18:23.530
[Outpatient Department of Yuanmei Community Health Center]

18:27.990 --> 18:29.630
You're sure the person

18:29.750 --> 18:30.590
in the photo

18:30.750 --> 18:31.630
took this bus

18:31.670 --> 18:32.880
and got off

18:32.950 --> 18:33.590
at Xincheng Garden,

18:34.190 --> 18:34.550
right?

18:34.550 --> 18:35.110
Yes, I'm sure.

18:35.550 --> 18:36.470
Okay, thank you.

18:35.880 --> 18:39.700
[Xincheng Garden Bus Station]

18:36.790 --> 18:37.310
Thank you.

18:40.500 --> 18:41.110
How did it go?

18:43.110 --> 18:43.550
It's confirmed.

18:43.590 --> 18:44.430
She took this bus

18:44.590 --> 18:46.270
and got off at Xincheng Garden.

18:49.750 --> 18:50.710
Let's check the cameras.

19:06.990 --> 19:11.390
[Garage Exit]

19:21.110 --> 19:22.950
So her last appearance

19:23.030 --> 19:24.270
was at this alley entrance, right?

19:25.860 --> 19:26.870
Are there any surveillance cameras inside?

19:27.470 --> 19:28.550
This is a desakota.

19:28.670 --> 19:29.910
It's all homesteads

19:30.350 --> 19:31.310
with houses

19:31.310 --> 19:32.630
built by the villagers.

19:32.910 --> 19:33.670
It's a mess.

19:33.710 --> 19:34.640
There aren't many surveillance cameras.

19:39.310 --> 19:40.550
Went in through this entrance.

19:42.270 --> 19:43.430
There are

19:44.910 --> 19:45.790
six exits in the area.

19:46.470 --> 19:47.110
Entering here,

19:47.270 --> 19:48.750
if she wants to go home,

19:49.990 --> 19:50.580
she should come out

19:50.580 --> 19:52.030
from the northwest corner.

19:50.840 --> 19:53.980
[Xinhua Village] [Homestead]

19:52.830 --> 19:53.350
Have you checked it?

19:54.030 --> 19:54.870
Yes.

19:54.950 --> 19:55.670
But now,

19:55.750 --> 19:57.310
we only have footage of her entering.

19:57.670 --> 19:58.870
Nothing of her exiting.

19:59.510 --> 20:00.870
The other five exits have been checked?

20:01.030 --> 20:01.510
Yes.

20:01.790 --> 20:02.590
No clues either.

20:03.470 --> 20:04.870
So she went missing

20:04.790 --> 20:07.330
[Xinhua Village] [Homestead]

20:05.270 --> 20:06.750
in this area.

20:07.630 --> 20:08.230
Here.

20:09.190 --> 20:11.310
Find all the cars

20:11.550 --> 20:12.190
that passed through

20:12.510 --> 20:13.720
these openings

20:13.720 --> 20:14.430
from the time

20:15.310 --> 20:15.990
she went in.

20:16.430 --> 20:17.190
We'll investigate them one by one tomorrow.

20:18.670 --> 20:19.670
Thank you,

20:19.670 --> 20:20.150
Mr. Liu.

20:20.310 --> 20:21.710
Please cooperate with us

20:21.750 --> 20:22.990
to check all the surrounding cameras.

20:23.150 --> 20:23.710
Alright.

20:23.780 --> 20:24.190
Thank you.

20:24.190 --> 20:24.750
It's okay.

20:27.620 --> 20:30.630
[Garage Exit] [Alley] [Alley A] [Bike Shed]

20:57.840 --> 20:59.580
[Exit] [Entrance]

21:12.830 --> 21:13.190
Senior.

21:13.630 --> 21:14.030
Senior!

21:14.990 --> 21:15.430
I've checked over there.

21:15.430 --> 21:15.990
There's nothing.

21:16.190 --> 21:18.230
But 20 meters in

21:18.390 --> 21:19.230
from the alley entrance,

21:19.350 --> 21:20.110
it's a surveillance blind spot.

21:20.310 --> 21:20.790
This side too.

21:20.960 --> 21:21.830
So there is

21:22.270 --> 21:23.270
a big blind spot in the middle.

21:23.480 --> 21:24.470
It's likely the crime scene.

21:25.550 --> 21:26.790
The CCTV at the alley entrance

21:26.830 --> 21:27.510
is this one right?

21:27.160 --> 21:33.350
[Exit] [Entrance]

21:27.510 --> 21:27.880
Yes.

21:30.590 --> 21:31.070
Let's look inside.

21:31.470 --> 21:31.830
Okay.

21:42.010 --> 21:45.430
[Trash Collection and Temporary Storage Point]

21:49.390 --> 21:51.310
If it's done here,

21:52.350 --> 21:53.720
residential buildings are on both sides.

21:54.710 --> 21:55.110
Senior,

21:55.230 --> 21:55.990
is there a possibility

21:56.110 --> 21:56.990
the suspect

21:56.990 --> 21:57.630
is very professional

21:57.790 --> 21:59.150
and quickly made

21:59.670 --> 22:01.390
Wang Qianqian lose consciousness?

22:01.990 --> 22:02.960
I'm not curious

22:03.070 --> 22:04.070
how he did it now.

22:04.110 --> 22:05.190
I'm curious

22:06.270 --> 22:08.030
how he just disappeared.

22:08.510 --> 22:09.670
He couldn't have flown away, could he?

22:12.430 --> 22:12.910
Here.

22:12.970 --> 22:16.710
[Trash Collection and Temporary Storage Point]

22:13.110 --> 22:14.390
Find and screen all cars,

22:14.390 --> 22:14.990
transportation vehicles,

22:15.190 --> 22:16.000
and even things

22:16.470 --> 22:17.190
that can carry people

22:17.340 --> 22:18.030
that go through

22:18.190 --> 22:19.350
all entrances

22:19.910 --> 22:21.110
connected to this alleyway.

22:21.590 --> 22:21.750
Yes.

22:21.910 --> 22:22.470
I...

22:22.950 --> 22:23.790
I'll have them screen it again.

22:27.640 --> 22:31.000
[Public Security]

22:32.270 --> 22:33.470
Officer,

22:33.710 --> 22:35.150
something happened to my girlfriend.

22:35.830 --> 22:36.790
Shouldn't you

22:36.790 --> 22:37.820
let me out?

22:37.990 --> 22:39.190
I'm innocent.

22:39.350 --> 22:39.950
Aren't you

22:39.950 --> 22:41.350
very humane?

22:43.430 --> 22:44.070
Zhang Xiaohui.

22:44.710 --> 22:45.350
You didn't cherish her

22:45.430 --> 22:46.350
when she was alive.

22:46.990 --> 22:47.830
Now she's dead

22:48.230 --> 22:48.760
and you're worried?

22:49.070 --> 22:49.870
I'm innocent.

22:50.110 --> 22:50.830
If you hadn't

22:50.830 --> 22:51.630
locked me up here,

22:51.720 --> 22:53.030
I could've gone out to protect her.

22:53.150 --> 22:54.710
She wouldn't have died, okay?

22:55.150 --> 22:55.470
Okay.

22:56.350 --> 22:57.110
Then answer

22:57.110 --> 22:57.750
my question.

22:58.440 --> 22:59.310
Half a month ago,

22:59.550 --> 23:00.270
you had a WeChat contact

23:00.300 --> 23:01.030
called Lin.

23:02.470 --> 23:02.950
You told him

23:03.030 --> 23:03.910
you had to teach your girlfriend

23:03.950 --> 23:04.590
a lesson.

23:04.990 --> 23:06.000
You transferred him 1,000 yuan.

23:06.750 --> 23:07.700
What for?

23:08.230 --> 23:09.390
Isn't it normal to pay

23:09.390 --> 23:11.190
when buying something?

23:12.030 --> 23:12.910
You still don't understand

23:12.990 --> 23:14.230
the seriousness of the matter?

23:14.670 --> 23:15.240
Listen.

23:15.470 --> 23:16.630
If we find out

23:16.870 --> 23:17.430
you hid something

23:17.470 --> 23:18.430
or covered up for others,

23:19.270 --> 23:20.510
your sentence will be different.

23:21.750 --> 23:22.630
Officer,

23:23.230 --> 23:23.750
do you think

23:23.790 --> 23:25.180
I hired a hitman?

23:25.590 --> 23:25.960
Okay.

23:26.190 --> 23:27.030
I'll give you 1,000 yuan.

23:27.070 --> 23:27.590
Hire one for me.

23:40.790 --> 23:41.670
Alright.

23:42.350 --> 23:43.150
Let me tell you.

23:43.190 --> 23:44.790
I bought a switchblade.

23:45.430 --> 23:46.820
What kind of switchblade costs 1,000 yuan?

23:47.270 --> 23:49.030
I collect switchblades.

23:49.430 --> 23:50.390
He said switchblades

23:50.390 --> 23:51.790
are regulated knives.

23:51.870 --> 23:52.750
It's hard to find.

23:53.030 --> 23:53.550
In the end,

23:53.790 --> 23:54.520
I paid him

23:54.830 --> 23:55.910
1,000 yuan

23:56.030 --> 23:57.270
and he blocked me.

23:57.510 --> 23:58.670
He is a liar.

23:58.790 --> 23:59.950
You should help me investigate.

24:05.390 --> 24:05.910
Officer,

24:06.790 --> 24:07.670
if I can tell you

24:07.740 --> 24:08.870
who the murderer is,

24:09.440 --> 24:10.030
can I

24:10.190 --> 24:10.870
redeem myself?

24:11.830 --> 24:12.190
Tell me.

24:13.230 --> 24:14.950
It must be Lu Yan from the hospital.

24:16.470 --> 24:17.830
She's always jealous of Qianqian

24:17.910 --> 24:18.990
having a good boyfriend like me.

24:19.150 --> 24:20.430
She's been trying to sow discord.

24:21.110 --> 24:21.990
She must be

24:22.070 --> 24:23.390
jealous of Qianqian,

24:23.910 --> 24:25.030
so she killed her.

24:27.750 --> 24:28.670
You can look into it.

24:30.430 --> 24:31.190
No, no, no.

24:31.720 --> 24:32.670
It should be the other one.

24:32.910 --> 24:33.430
The one

24:33.630 --> 24:34.470
who hit me last time.

24:35.230 --> 24:36.430
The one who asked you to catch me

24:36.470 --> 24:37.150
after that?

24:41.070 --> 24:41.590
No.

24:42.190 --> 24:43.310
It might be the...

24:44.510 --> 24:45.910
The one who delivered the food last time.

24:47.270 --> 24:48.190
And another

24:48.230 --> 24:49.230
tall boy.

24:50.790 --> 24:52.190
Don't look at me.

24:52.310 --> 24:54.110
Go and investigate, okay?

25:02.630 --> 25:03.150
Senior,

25:03.270 --> 25:04.310
I'll go back

25:04.430 --> 25:05.550
and screen these license plate numbers.

25:06.190 --> 25:06.670
Okay.

25:07.270 --> 25:07.750
Thank you.

25:07.980 --> 25:08.390
It's my job.

25:08.510 --> 25:08.990
I'm leaving.

25:09.150 --> 25:09.430
Bye.

25:44.310 --> 25:45.070
Hello, Captain Jiang.

25:45.510 --> 25:45.790
Hello.

25:46.510 --> 25:47.150
Matron Qiao.

25:47.990 --> 25:49.070
How is Lu Yan?

25:50.990 --> 25:52.150
She didn’t go home today.

25:52.790 --> 25:53.950
She's working now.

25:55.590 --> 25:56.710
We can see that

25:56.830 --> 25:57.550
she is in a

25:57.710 --> 25:58.430
state of stress.

25:58.910 --> 25:59.910
She's still holding up on the surface.

26:01.000 --> 26:01.640
But actually,

26:02.630 --> 26:03.310
she's avoiding it.

26:05.640 --> 26:06.230
Don't worry.

26:06.750 --> 26:07.750
We'll be with her.

26:10.150 --> 26:10.470
Okay.

26:11.350 --> 26:11.750
Well,

26:12.150 --> 26:12.900
thank you.

26:25.060 --> 26:33.550
[Anesthesiology Department Duty Room]

26:37.110 --> 26:37.630
Lu.

26:39.190 --> 26:39.910
You don't want to go home?

26:41.470 --> 26:42.310
Matron Qiao.

26:43.700 --> 26:44.550
I want to

26:45.710 --> 26:47.230
stay here for a while.

26:52.590 --> 26:53.300
That's great.

26:54.710 --> 26:55.640
Then

26:55.670 --> 26:56.480
we'll spend the night together.

26:56.910 --> 26:57.550
I'll sleep on the upper bunk.

26:57.670 --> 26:58.340
You sleep on the lower bunk.

26:59.200 --> 27:00.750
Don't you need to go home?

27:02.270 --> 27:03.070
I was just told

27:03.110 --> 27:03.630
that

27:03.750 --> 27:04.790
my power went out tonight.

27:05.060 --> 27:06.110
It'll be too troublesome for me to go back.

27:11.070 --> 27:11.350
Here.

27:12.190 --> 27:12.870
I'll make the bed for you.

27:13.360 --> 27:18.190
[Anesthesiology Department Duty Room]

27:14.100 --> 27:14.790
Rest early.

27:18.630 --> 27:19.190
Matron Qiao.

27:21.070 --> 27:21.580
Thank you.

27:23.550 --> 27:24.270
For what?

27:25.550 --> 27:26.510
I'm afraid

27:26.830 --> 27:27.950
I'll wake you up at night

27:28.230 --> 27:28.750
because I snore

27:29.030 --> 27:29.710
and grind my teeth.

27:35.190 --> 27:37.240
Come, rest early.

27:39.470 --> 27:39.840
Here.

27:44.070 --> 27:47.020
[Public Security]

27:47.030 --> 27:47.910
if I can tell you

27:47.450 --> 27:51.270
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

27:47.990 --> 27:49.110
who the murderer is,

27:49.630 --> 27:50.310
can I

27:50.390 --> 27:51.190
redeem myself?

27:52.390 --> 27:54.070
It must be Lu Yan from the hospital.

27:54.680 --> 27:55.990
She's always jealous of Qianqian

27:56.030 --> 27:57.150
having a good boyfriend like me.

27:57.350 --> 27:58.430
She's been trying to sow discord.

27:58.990 --> 28:00.030
She must be

28:00.030 --> 28:01.270
jealous of Qianqian,

28:01.790 --> 28:02.670
so she killed her.

28:04.470 --> 28:05.750
Zhang Xiaohui

28:06.190 --> 28:07.990
is timid in character but aggressive.

28:08.270 --> 28:09.350
Isn't he the typical kind we say

28:09.470 --> 28:10.910
that has the heart of a thief but not the guts?

28:11.230 --> 28:12.500
But he tried to

28:12.710 --> 28:14.110
hurt Wang Qianqian with a knife before.

28:15.630 --> 28:16.470
Violence is

28:16.550 --> 28:17.910
the most primitive means of control

28:18.230 --> 28:19.790
and one of the lowest forms.

28:20.110 --> 28:21.950
Those who choose this way

28:22.510 --> 28:25.030
are usually self-abased and cowardly.

28:26.030 --> 28:27.270
I think Zhang Xiaohui

28:27.440 --> 28:28.190
has nothing to do

28:28.310 --> 28:29.150
Wang Qianqian's death.

28:30.110 --> 28:31.110
You didn't find

28:31.230 --> 28:32.430
the evidence of his contract killing, right?

28:39.510 --> 28:40.390
Officer Yu is back?

28:41.030 --> 28:41.350
Captain Jiang.

28:41.500 --> 28:42.310
Hello, Officer Yu.

28:42.470 --> 28:43.350
I asked Officer Yu

28:43.470 --> 28:44.550
to analyze Zhang Xiaohui.

28:46.950 --> 28:47.790
I think

28:47.990 --> 28:48.950
he has nothing to do

28:49.110 --> 28:50.350
with Wang Qianqian's case.

28:50.710 --> 28:51.230
Why?

28:53.230 --> 28:54.310
I read the file.

28:54.790 --> 28:56.510
The murderer is extremely cruel

28:56.710 --> 28:57.870
and meticulous.

28:58.150 --> 28:58.910
I think

28:59.160 --> 28:59.950
you must have

29:00.030 --> 29:00.990
a hard time this time.

29:01.350 --> 29:01.830
Indeed.

29:02.270 --> 29:04.270
This person is very good at counter-surveillance.

29:05.480 --> 29:05.950
But there's one thing

29:05.950 --> 29:07.110
I find strange.

29:07.950 --> 29:08.910
Why didn't he

29:08.950 --> 29:10.310
take care of this bag?

29:11.070 --> 29:11.630
Such a

29:11.670 --> 29:12.990
meticulous murderer

29:13.430 --> 29:14.750
could clean the hair

29:14.750 --> 29:16.030
and fingerprints so well.

29:16.790 --> 29:17.790
Then why did he leave a bag

29:17.790 --> 29:18.470
at the scene?

29:20.390 --> 29:21.790
Unless...

29:22.710 --> 29:23.270
It was on purpose?

29:24.590 --> 29:25.070
Yes.

29:26.270 --> 29:27.300
Unless this clue

29:27.350 --> 29:28.670
was left it to the police on purpose,

29:29.750 --> 29:30.830
hoping we could find

29:30.870 --> 29:32.190
Wang Qianqian's body as soon as possible.

29:33.550 --> 29:34.830
What kind of murderer

29:34.950 --> 29:35.630
and what kind of

29:35.670 --> 29:36.870
criminal psychology and motive

29:37.230 --> 29:38.590
would hope the police could find

29:38.710 --> 29:39.950
the body as soon as possible?

29:41.550 --> 29:42.390
This is so strange.

29:42.590 --> 29:43.470
It doesn't match

29:43.630 --> 29:44.990
the logic of murder and dumping the body.

29:49.780 --> 29:50.070
Yes.

29:52.790 --> 29:53.030
Okay.

29:53.590 --> 29:53.950
What’s wrong?

29:54.310 --> 29:54.590
Captain Jiang,

29:54.950 --> 29:55.790
Wang Qianqian's phone data

29:55.790 --> 29:56.350
has been restored.

29:56.470 --> 29:57.470
It has been uploaded.

29:58.070 --> 29:58.550
Open it.

29:58.710 --> 29:59.070
Okay.

30:02.100 --> 30:04.800
[Wang Qianqian's Phone Album]

30:02.630 --> 30:04.030
This man is called Yu Bofeng.

30:04.950 --> 30:05.990
He debuted from an idol survival show.

30:06.400 --> 30:07.070
He's quite famous.

30:07.290 --> 30:10.110
[Wang Qianqian's Phone Album]

30:12.320 --> 30:15.490
[Wang Qianqian's Phone Album]

30:16.380 --> 30:17.350
Wang Qianqian was

30:17.590 --> 30:18.160
a fan?

30:19.670 --> 30:21.390
If she was a fan,

30:21.710 --> 30:22.270
these people

30:22.270 --> 30:23.430
usually have many side accounts.

30:23.750 --> 30:24.830
You can search online.

30:25.230 --> 30:27.150
Could they be friends

30:27.470 --> 30:28.270
or classmates?

30:30.590 --> 30:32.470
Have you found

30:32.510 --> 30:33.150
her WeChat history?

30:33.430 --> 30:33.830
Yes.

30:36.030 --> 30:36.880
[Wang Qianqian's WeChat History]

30:37.420 --> 30:38.990
[Wen Peng]

30:42.290 --> 30:43.590
[Wen Peng]

30:44.390 --> 30:46.990
[He is so handsome in person.]

30:44.390 --> 30:46.990
[Hahaha, it's real. It's nothing. He happens to have time.]

30:44.390 --> 30:46.990
[Mr. Wen, thank you for taking me to see Yu Bofeng. You made a fan's dream come true. It feels unreal.]

30:51.230 --> 30:53.510
9:45 P.M.

30:54.030 --> 30:54.590
Wen Peng.

31:00.070 --> 31:00.950
Who is Wen Peng?

31:10.990 --> 31:11.350
Wen,

31:12.070 --> 31:13.820
I read the character's biography.

31:14.510 --> 31:15.670
I really love it.

31:16.070 --> 31:17.230
He's a killer.

31:17.710 --> 31:18.150
And also

31:18.350 --> 31:19.590
he's not an ordinary killer.

31:20.430 --> 31:21.470
He was hurt

31:21.630 --> 31:23.110
by his family,

31:23.310 --> 31:24.310
which made his character's

31:24.470 --> 31:25.630
growth and transformation arc very interesting.

31:25.950 --> 31:26.550
Are you sure?

31:27.350 --> 31:28.670
This movie takes eight months.

31:29.350 --> 31:30.270
And it's the lead antagonist.

31:30.550 --> 31:31.750
You definitely won't be the leading actor.

31:33.110 --> 31:33.790
I don't care.

31:34.510 --> 31:34.870
Wen,

31:35.390 --> 31:36.590
my dream is to play

31:36.750 --> 31:38.070
a role that can be remembered by the audience.

31:41.160 --> 31:41.510
Wen,

31:41.790 --> 31:42.390
please help me.

31:42.590 --> 31:43.470
I really like

31:43.510 --> 31:44.110
this role.

31:44.550 --> 31:45.310
Please help me get it.

31:47.110 --> 31:47.430
Sure.

31:47.750 --> 31:49.030
I'll find you

31:49.230 --> 31:50.510
a professor in criminal psychology.

31:50.790 --> 31:51.950
You can study well

31:52.070 --> 31:53.750
and then go to Director Wang.

31:54.990 --> 31:55.440
Thank you.

31:59.270 --> 31:59.710
Mr. Wen,

32:00.190 --> 32:01.670
a police surnamed Jiang is looking for you.

32:02.310 --> 32:02.950
Police?

32:06.590 --> 32:07.200
Let them in.

32:07.750 --> 32:08.110
Okay.

32:09.230 --> 32:10.310
Why are the police looking for us?

32:15.310 --> 32:15.870
Mr. Wen.

32:16.550 --> 32:17.310
What's with the crowd?

32:19.550 --> 32:20.440
Excuse us.

32:20.670 --> 32:21.350
Mere formality.

32:21.550 --> 32:22.390
I have to show you my badge.

32:22.710 --> 32:23.190
[Public Security]

32:23.550 --> 32:24.910
Anshan Criminal Investigation Unit.

32:25.430 --> 32:26.870
We have some questions for you.

32:27.230 --> 32:27.710
Are you free?

32:28.550 --> 32:29.590
Sure, no problem.

32:31.310 --> 32:31.670
Sit.

32:32.230 --> 32:32.580
Wen.

32:33.710 --> 32:34.470
I'll leave then.

32:35.230 --> 32:35.590
Okay.

32:37.190 --> 32:38.590
Yu Bofeng, right?

32:40.270 --> 32:40.870
Just in time.

32:41.470 --> 32:42.270
We need you too.

32:43.270 --> 32:44.230
Talk to him alone.

32:45.510 --> 32:46.230
Let's go, superstar.

32:49.590 --> 32:54.360
[Future]

32:51.670 --> 32:52.430
Mr. Yu Bofeng.

32:52.950 --> 32:54.110
Do you know Wang Qianqian?

32:54.680 --> 32:55.470
Wang Qianqian?

32:58.430 --> 32:58.950
No.

33:01.650 --> 33:05.680
[Future]

33:02.950 --> 33:03.390
This person.

33:07.830 --> 33:09.100
I really don't know her.

33:10.550 --> 33:11.550
Take a good look.

33:12.960 --> 33:13.670
Don't you remember?

33:20.430 --> 33:21.510
She's your fan.

33:21.830 --> 33:22.630
My fan?

33:24.150 --> 33:25.950
But I have too many fans.

33:26.070 --> 33:26.580
I can't remember

33:26.630 --> 33:27.910
all my fans' names.

33:32.750 --> 33:33.630
Do you remember now?

33:38.830 --> 33:39.830
I only remember after you

33:39.950 --> 33:40.670
showed me this picture.

33:40.990 --> 33:42.110
This is a friend of my boss.

33:42.310 --> 33:43.470
We had a meal together

33:43.640 --> 33:44.310
at my boss's club.

33:44.680 --> 33:45.830
We had a great time that night

33:45.990 --> 33:47.150
and took this photo.

33:47.470 --> 33:48.910
You had dinner with her

33:49.270 --> 33:50.030
and took photos together,

33:50.710 --> 33:52.110
but you don't even remember her name.

33:52.470 --> 33:53.390
I go out every day

33:53.430 --> 33:54.510
and have to meet many people.

33:54.710 --> 33:55.400
I can't manage to

33:55.550 --> 33:56.950
remember everyone's name.

33:57.550 --> 33:58.030
Besides,

33:58.030 --> 33:58.710
my fans and I

33:58.790 --> 33:59.870
take photos like this.

34:01.510 --> 34:02.030
Well,

34:02.350 --> 34:03.950
did something happen to this girl?

34:05.350 --> 34:05.750
I'm sorry.

34:06.110 --> 34:06.790
Our case

34:06.870 --> 34:07.630
is still confidential.

34:08.310 --> 34:08.830
Let me ask you.

34:09.550 --> 34:10.699
Where you were after 9 P.M.

34:11.230 --> 34:11.800
two nights ago?

34:12.230 --> 34:12.909
Two nights ago?

34:12.949 --> 34:13.270
Yes.

34:14.909 --> 34:16.000
Let me check my schedule.

34:20.630 --> 34:21.880
I was shooting an ad two nights ago

34:21.989 --> 34:23.070
until 10 P.M.

34:23.429 --> 34:24.830
Then I went to my boss's celebration party.

34:25.750 --> 34:26.790
So,

34:27.550 --> 34:28.750
people at

34:28.989 --> 34:30.310
the ad shoot and celebration party

34:30.750 --> 34:31.989
can be your alibi?

34:32.340 --> 34:33.110
Of course.

34:33.389 --> 34:33.909
My boss

34:33.989 --> 34:34.949
and assistant were all there.

34:36.550 --> 34:37.710
Did you meet each other

34:37.750 --> 34:38.480
since the last time?

34:39.150 --> 34:39.550
No.

34:40.360 --> 34:41.750
Did you exchange each other's contact information?

34:42.230 --> 34:43.389
That's even more impossible.

34:44.949 --> 34:45.270
Okay.

34:45.870 --> 34:46.750
Please understand.

34:47.590 --> 34:48.830
We have a few questions.

34:50.510 --> 34:52.389
Do you know Wang Qianqian?

34:53.270 --> 34:53.790
Yes.

34:55.590 --> 34:56.350
What's your relationship?

34:57.070 --> 34:57.990
I guess we're friends.

34:58.590 --> 34:59.670
How do you

35:00.320 --> 35:01.060
know each other?

35:01.950 --> 35:02.630
Through Lu Yan.

35:03.110 --> 35:04.430
I have a good relationship with Lu Yan.

35:07.190 --> 35:08.430
Do you have any personal relationship with Wang Qianqian?

35:12.990 --> 35:13.950
I found her a house.

35:15.670 --> 35:16.550
Found her a house?

35:18.400 --> 35:20.070
That means you're close.

35:22.470 --> 35:23.670
Because she's Lu Yan's friend.

35:23.950 --> 35:24.780
I was just helping.

35:28.590 --> 35:30.470
On December 4th,

35:30.830 --> 35:32.020
the day before yesterday,

35:32.880 --> 35:35.990
what were you doing between 9 P.M.

35:37.030 --> 35:37.750
and 12 A.M.?

35:38.270 --> 35:39.150
December 4th.

35:39.230 --> 35:40.390
It was the premiere.

35:40.590 --> 35:41.390
I was with

35:41.470 --> 35:42.590
my company team.

35:43.470 --> 35:44.230
When did you finish?

35:45.470 --> 35:46.990
I think around 11.

35:47.800 --> 35:48.910
Where were you after that?

35:50.430 --> 35:51.190
After that,

35:51.510 --> 35:52.950
I had a drink

35:53.310 --> 35:54.030
with the film crew.

35:54.910 --> 35:55.870
My artist went too.

35:56.030 --> 35:56.670
Yu Bofeng.

35:56.950 --> 35:57.790
He can testify for me.

35:59.950 --> 36:00.910
When did it last until?

36:01.710 --> 36:02.470
When did you get home?

36:05.150 --> 36:06.150
I drank a lot that day.

36:06.310 --> 36:08.900
I think it was around 2 or 3 A.M.

36:11.760 --> 36:12.870
That night,

36:13.350 --> 36:14.150
Wang Qianqian

36:14.310 --> 36:15.390
called you, right?

36:17.270 --> 36:17.910
What did you talk about?

36:18.830 --> 36:19.710
She told me

36:19.870 --> 36:21.550
she was sorry she didn't come to the premiere.

36:21.590 --> 36:22.230
And...

36:24.230 --> 36:25.230
Some casual small talk.

36:25.870 --> 36:26.470
And then?

36:28.150 --> 36:28.870
And then...

36:29.270 --> 36:30.270
Nothing.

36:31.310 --> 36:32.150
Anything else?

36:34.910 --> 36:36.710
I asked her to meet

36:36.780 --> 36:38.030
with my artist, Yu Bofeng, once.

36:38.510 --> 36:40.790
I invited Wang Qianqian

36:41.230 --> 36:42.190
and Lu Yan.

36:43.510 --> 36:44.870
But there was a small incident.

36:45.430 --> 36:46.030
Please tell us.

36:46.670 --> 36:48.350
Can't you find out?

36:50.670 --> 36:51.470
We are working.

36:52.670 --> 36:53.390
Please tell us.

36:54.790 --> 36:56.630
He should be

36:56.920 --> 36:58.070
Wang Qianqian's boyfriend.

36:58.310 --> 36:59.630
He suddenly barged into my club.

36:59.790 --> 37:00.310
Then...

37:02.550 --> 37:03.710
How should I put it? We had a fight.

37:04.790 --> 37:06.070
There was some blood,

37:06.510 --> 37:07.580
but it's all good now.

37:07.870 --> 37:08.550
It's been taken care of.

37:09.470 --> 37:10.310
Anything else?

37:12.990 --> 37:13.430
No.

37:14.870 --> 37:15.180
Okay.

37:16.390 --> 37:17.350
Thank you for your cooperation.

37:17.630 --> 37:18.820
I'll ask you anytime if there's anything else.

37:21.110 --> 37:21.670
Captain Jiang.

37:22.870 --> 37:23.670
Did something

37:23.750 --> 37:24.750
happen to Wang Qianqian?

37:26.110 --> 37:26.760
Nothing.

37:27.510 --> 37:28.630
You don't need to know now.

37:31.830 --> 37:32.750
I hope everything is fine.

37:33.550 --> 37:34.870
Otherwise, Lu Yan will be upset again.

37:41.230 --> 37:41.880
We’re leaving.

37:43.070 --> 37:43.540
Thank you.

37:44.950 --> 37:45.430
Thank you.

37:56.830 --> 37:57.270
Captain Jiang,

37:57.550 --> 37:58.830
we asked around the company.

37:59.230 --> 38:00.110
Wen Peng and Yu Bofeng

38:00.190 --> 38:01.230
both have an alibi.

38:03.030 --> 38:03.630
What do you think?

38:04.510 --> 38:05.430
I think Yu Bofeng

38:05.510 --> 38:06.880
has nothing to do with this case.

38:07.190 --> 38:07.870
Most importantly,

38:08.110 --> 38:08.910
he has no motive.

38:12.790 --> 38:13.590
Let's go back first.

38:14.270 --> 38:15.230
See Officer Yu off.

38:15.270 --> 38:15.630
Okay.

38:16.430 --> 38:17.110
See you.

38:18.270 --> 38:19.070
Call me if you need anything.

38:27.070 --> 38:27.660
Director Xing.

38:32.150 --> 38:32.950
Okay, I got it.

38:58.070 --> 38:58.510
Hello?

38:59.230 --> 38:59.590
Hello?

39:00.990 --> 39:01.430
Lu Yan.

39:03.550 --> 39:04.430
We've communicated

39:04.880 --> 39:06.550
with Wang Qianqian's parents.

39:07.670 --> 39:08.630
She'll be sent

39:08.670 --> 39:09.710
to the funeral home today.

39:13.110 --> 39:14.100
Do you want to

39:16.350 --> 39:17.480
see her one last time?

39:19.550 --> 39:20.230
I know you are

39:20.270 --> 39:21.350
very upset

39:21.750 --> 39:22.590
and conflicted.

39:26.590 --> 39:27.630
But I'm worried

39:29.710 --> 39:30.950
you might regret

39:32.630 --> 39:33.750
not seeing her for the last time.

39:35.670 --> 39:36.400
Do you need it?

39:42.350 --> 39:42.790
Okay.

39:44.390 --> 39:45.000
Okay.

39:47.350 --> 39:47.750
Okay.

40:30.570 --> 40:36.720
[Morgue]

40:36.990 --> 40:37.910
I've talked to

40:37.950 --> 40:38.510
Wang Qianqian's parents.

40:38.750 --> 40:39.870
They agreed for Dr. Lu

40:39.950 --> 40:40.670
to see Wang Qianqian.

40:41.190 --> 40:41.500
Okay.

40:42.110 --> 40:42.670
Call me if you need anything.

40:43.000 --> 40:43.550
Thank you.

40:53.470 --> 40:54.190
Let me take you in.

41:28.870 --> 41:29.550
Open it.

41:41.070 --> 41:43.800
[Strictly confidential] [No photos or videos allowed]

41:47.950 --> 41:49.150
You scared me.

41:49.430 --> 41:50.110
You haven't eaten, have you?

41:50.390 --> 41:51.070
This is the breakfast

41:51.150 --> 41:52.350
I made for you.

41:52.670 --> 41:54.310
This is so cute!

41:54.470 --> 41:55.070
Isn't it amazing?

41:55.190 --> 41:56.110
Yes, let me try one.

41:56.170 --> 42:02.000
[Outpatient Ward]

41:56.420 --> 41:57.550
Wang Qianqian,

41:57.750 --> 41:58.590
I'm telling you.

41:59.110 --> 42:00.190
Stop clinging to me.

42:00.430 --> 42:01.750
Matron Qiao said

42:02.110 --> 42:03.630
we can't keep doing this. It's bad influence.

42:03.910 --> 42:04.710
What?

42:04.870 --> 42:05.830
It's break time.

42:05.870 --> 42:07.230
I just want to cling to you.

42:07.390 --> 42:08.550
Fine.

42:09.030 --> 42:09.470
Yan,

42:10.110 --> 42:10.510
look!

42:10.790 --> 42:11.790
Look at my prince charming's new photo.

42:12.030 --> 42:13.230
Isn't he handsome?

42:13.510 --> 42:14.230
Also,

42:14.510 --> 42:14.950
his movie

42:15.110 --> 42:15.830
will be released soon.

42:16.030 --> 42:16.910
I can watch the premiere.

42:17.070 --> 42:17.960
I'll be able to see him.

42:18.630 --> 42:19.750
I'm so happy!

42:20.350 --> 42:20.870
I really...

42:22.360 --> 42:23.790
I can see him in person.

42:28.590 --> 42:28.990
Yan,

42:29.590 --> 42:30.110
you must be tired.

42:30.360 --> 42:31.030
Drink some water.

42:32.250 --> 42:35.660
[Operating Room]

42:32.550 --> 42:33.150
Later,

42:33.190 --> 42:34.350
what delicious food should we eat?

42:35.710 --> 42:36.670
What do you want to eat?

42:46.950 --> 42:48.990
Smells good.

42:49.750 --> 42:50.190
Here.

42:52.190 --> 42:52.950
It smells so good.

42:53.910 --> 42:55.030
You even added sausage for me?

42:55.100 --> 42:55.940
Of course.

42:56.190 --> 42:56.910
I spoil you, right?

43:22.390 --> 43:24.550
Happy birthday, Man.

43:24.550 --> 43:25.550
Thank you.

43:25.790 --> 43:26.870
Let's take a photo together.

43:27.150 --> 43:27.350
Okay.

43:27.590 --> 43:28.190
Let's take a photo.

43:30.390 --> 43:31.510
We prepared for so long

43:31.550 --> 43:32.390
to hide it and give you a

43:32.430 --> 43:33.190
surprise.

43:33.910 --> 43:34.870
Wait a minute.

43:37.270 --> 43:37.590
Come on.

43:37.630 --> 43:38.670
Change your expression.

43:38.990 --> 43:40.630
Three, two, one.

43:45.980 --> 43:48.520
[Morgue]

43:50.710 --> 43:51.310
Lu Yan.

43:52.500 --> 43:53.690
[Morgue]

43:52.950 --> 43:53.350
Are you okay?

43:53.870 --> 43:54.350
Yes.

44:05.080 --> 44:08.960
[Morgue]

44:14.620 --> 44:17.380
[Morgue]

44:21.560 --> 44:22.990
[No outside objects are allowed into the morgue]

45:59.430 --> 46:00.550
Stop following me.

46:04.990 --> 46:05.550
I'm sorry.

46:05.750 --> 46:07.190
I can't look at you now.

46:07.670 --> 46:08.710
Because when I see you,

46:08.790 --> 46:10.270
I'll think of

46:12.950 --> 46:13.830
how I was

46:13.910 --> 46:15.550
with you that night.

46:15.710 --> 46:16.430
That's why

46:17.110 --> 46:18.190
I couldn't...

46:19.070 --> 46:21.030
I couldn't answer her call.

46:21.030 --> 46:22.990
I didn't save her!

46:26.790 --> 46:28.470
I'm not blaming you.

46:32.430 --> 46:33.350
I just think

46:33.390 --> 46:35.230
I'm very emotionally unstable.

46:35.390 --> 46:37.310
I don't know how to fix it.

46:37.840 --> 46:38.430
I don't know

46:38.430 --> 46:40.110
how to face our relationship.

46:47.030 --> 46:47.920
From now on...

46:53.750 --> 46:54.670
You should live your life

46:54.870 --> 46:56.030
and I'll live mine.

47:01.950 --> 47:03.660
Let's not contact each other anymore.

47:05.230 --> 47:05.830
I'm sorry.
